09/2013 EDB 0.8 released

05/04/2014 spark demo 

Demo steps. 
Reference of mingxiwu/edb/blob/edb0.8/project/config

Launch Hadoop
===============
cd /server/hadoop/bin/
tart-all.sh
hadoop fs -ls /
To see hdfs and job tracker in browser.

http://127.0.0.1:50070
http://127.0.0.1:50030

Launch Spark
==============
cd /server/spark-0.8_incubator
check  config/spark-env.sh

./bin/start-all.sh //this will start 3 workers.

check:
http://127.0.0.1:8080/
we should see 3 workers.

Launch EDB
============
cd /server/edb/core/target/scala-2.9.3

java -cp core-assembly-0.0.1.jar -Dspark.akka.frameSize=2000 -Dspark.shuffle.compress=true 
-Dlog4j.configuration=/server/spark/conf/log4j.properties edb.shell.edbMain

This will start edb shell.

- show tables //show all tables
- desc abc //describe table named abc
- select count(*) from abc
- select * from abc
- create table test2 (a int, b string)
- generate table test2 10 //this will genearte 10 records
- select * from test2
- select m, sum(id) from abc group by m

//I have done the following

create a tmp catalog folder
cd /tmp/ 
mkdir /tmp/edb
chmod 777 /tmp/edb


Shut down demo
===============
-stop hadoop
-ps -u mwu, kill spark, a java process




